Text:
JUST BEFORE INSTALLING THE MOD, MAKE SURE THE SETTINGS OF YOUR WARCRAFT MUST BE SET TO HIGH-ESPECIALLY THE VIDEO SETTINGS.
YOU MAY LATER ON LOWER THESE SETTINGS: PARTICLES, LIGHTS, OCCLUSION, UNIT SHADOWS. OTHER THAN THESE MAY NOT BE LOWERED AND IF LOWERED, MAY CAUSE GAME ERRORS.

-facelockmo
